# TOCS Core Rules

- TOCS is Formula First Architecture.
- Formula is the source of truth.
- Never create Deal, Order, Project, Pipeline as top-level entities.
- Formula 1 = Item 1.
- Company has no fixed role.
- Role is determined inside formula_participants.
- Payment structure must support schedules and records.
- Confirmed revenue is based on real bank deposits.
- Confirmed profit is based on real deposits and withdrawals.
- Status must not be auto-completed. Users manually complete/cancel status.
- Invoice is not a transaction blocker, but Formula cannot close without invoice completion.
- Do not add postponed V1 features unless explicitly approved.
